## SERP ANALYSIS

### Competitor Summary

**Common H2 topics competitors cover (baseline only):**
- What are whimsigoth nails / what is the aesthetic
- Whimsigoth nail colours (black, purple, burgundy, deep plum)
- Celestial motifs (moons, stars, constellations)
- Texture techniques (velvet polish, chrome, metallic outlines)
- Nail shape for whimsigoth (coffin, almond, stiletto)
- 3D elements and embellishments
